title: Chicken & Veggie Korma Curry Pie with Mash Potato Topping
description: A curry pie is the blend of two perfect warm dishes coming together to deliver us a hearty dinner. Korma curry is peppered with chicken and a rich variety of veggies like leek and spinach, with a potato mash top to hold all the delicious flavours in a pie that will surely be gobbled up in no time.

